author: DJI
description:
🎖 Social Media Selection Award – Weekly Winner
This film is dedicated to every drone lover and DJI creator. 

Thank you for filling the past year with countless moments of vision, courage, and creativity — and for shaping a global community that continues to see the world differently, from above.

In 2025, we didn’t just travel—we learned how to see the world again, together, with a drone. From the first light touching the Dolomites in Italy, to the Northern Lights dancing over Icelandic skies, and the moments of quiet romance shared in Türkiye, some places felt like the edge of the world, while others reminded us how alive it truly is. 

The film was created over countless hours of travel, waiting, and flying—using DJI Mavic 4 Pro, a flagship drone built for creators who tell stories across cultures, landscapes, and light.
